Record Class DynamicEnum.EnumValue

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.dua3.license.DynamicEnum.EnumValue
Record Components:
ordinal - the ordinal position of this value in the dynamic enum
name - the name of this value
value - the string representation of this value
parent - the dynamic enum instance to which this value belongs
Enclosing class:
DynamicEnum
public static record DynamicEnum.EnumValue(int ordinal, String name, String value, DynamicEnum parent) extends Record
Represents a value in a dynamically generated enum-like structure. Each instance of this record encapsulates the ordinal value, the name, and the corresponding value of the enum entry. It also maintains a reference to the parent DynamicEnum.
